            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the<strong> </strong>spring onion has softened, add the <strong>arborio rice</strong> and <strong>chopped garlic</strong> to the pan with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 1 min, stirring to coat the grains in oil</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
