    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>vegetable stock</strong> a ladle at a time, stirring continuously for 25-30 min or until all of the stock is absorbed and the rice is cooked</p><p>Reboil a kettle</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1117.-step-5-x200.jpg",
